History:
========


	1.0 (2/2/96) first public release.

	1.1 (11/2/96) 
		a reset problem fixed:
		 when the control (capslock or F12), left amiga (ctrl) and an another 
		 key are pressed together a reset occur. (OOOPS !).

		I have add some ugly pictures (screen snapshots) just to give a preview...


	1.2 (27/5/96)
		change some key mapping, see doc/otherStuf.txt for more.

    ...

	2.0 (06/6/96) Malor update

		Windows 95's new keyboard support (may be de/activated by a switch). 

		New mapping of the xtra Pc keys: F11, F12, inser, PageUp, PageDown, home, 
		end, printScreen, scrollLock.
		Added a switch to toggle between my key mapping or sending rawkey codes 
		for these xtra keys.

        Can perform a reset automatically after a delay.
        (A way to solve slow hard drive spin up problem !!!!!!!!)

\ Charles